WEBVTT
Kind: descriptions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.500
The screen shows a dark, snow-covered landscape at night.
A small illuminated window glows in a distant building.

00:00:04.500 --> 00:00:10.000
Cut to the interior of a sparse radio room.
Banks of equipment line the walls, dials glowing amber.

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:27.000
A waveform spikes on a monitor as the distorted voice plays.
Marcus leans forward, hand hovering over the recording button.

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:39.000
Close-up of Marcus's face, lit from below by screen light.
His expression shifts from boredom to sharp attention.

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:52.000
Marcus rises from his chair and moves to a second console,
fingers moving quickly across the keyboard.
